{"tid":621388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德貨車撞群眾多人死傷　司機自轟亡","createTime":"2018-04-08T09:27:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T10:43:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"237ca698a05026182337f2b8c23c627d0d8eaa0e","tid":621388,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:27:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180408/20355189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180408%2F20355189&d=c0cgvjwHXMmVisdxPFAbKGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=f26fdd60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180408%2F20355189&h=c4b2327f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180408/20355189</a><br />\n<br />\n德貨車撞群眾多人死傷　司機自轟亡<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞   <br />\n         <br />\n德國西部城市明斯特（Muenster）昨日發生汽車撞擊途人事件。消息指，一輛小型貨車在市內行人路上衝撞人群，釀成多人死傷，司機當場吞槍自盡。當局仍在調查事故起因，初步推測是恐怖襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180408/large/a1104a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180408%2Flarge%2Fa1104a.gif&h=3b7c6f51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n案發現場一片凌亂。<br />\n<br />\n初步推測是恐襲<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地下午，明斯特警方發言人指，這宗車撞人事故導致「數人身亡，包括疑兇」，確實死傷人數仍有待確定。德媒《明鏡周刊》就引述消息指，事件造成至少3人死亡、30人受傷。肇事者在現場開槍自轟身亡。<br />\n<br />\n當局現正「假定」事件是恐襲，但呼籲民眾避免猜疑。大批消防及救護車趕赴現場，警員在現場搜索是否有爆炸品，並呼籲民眾避免前往或離開市中心。歐洲近年接二連三發生汽車撞人襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n前年12月，德國柏林一名男子於聖誕市集內駕車撞死12人，另有56人受傷。 同年7月，法國尼斯舉行國慶慶祝活動途中，一名男子駕大型貨車衝向人群，造成86死、458人傷。去年6月，英國倫敦橋上一輛小型貨車衝向行人，車上3名男子下車向行人揮刀亂斬，事件中8人死亡、48人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n德新社/德國《明鏡周刊》"},{"pid":"eae1f9b59964eb5ef368614be9d965485cf3c3b6","tid":621388,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:35:37.000Z","msg":"清光蛔豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11c8402377a81f641e10b66d83310ef42442ee1","tid":621388,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:36:30.000Z","msg":"左膠又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a87bc61a2bf892169b579595066f70dd69483c","tid":621388,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:35:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f2cec5eecac91e54b54c5ba50e6d379a33a72d8","tid":621388,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:41:38.000Z","msg":"Local media reports identified the perpetrator as an industrial designer living in M&uuml;nster who had been suffering from psychological problems. The police, however, did not confirm those details.<br />\n<br />\nAccording to reports, the perpetrator had vaguely announced suicide plans in an email sent to friends a week ago. He was apparently also known to authorities for previous acts of violence as well as drug violations, which the police could not confirm Sunday.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.dw.com/en/germany-still-clueless-about-motive-for-fatal-van-attack-in-m%C3%BCnster/a-43297880\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.dw.com%2Fen%2Fgermany-still-clueless-about-motive-for-fatal-van-attack-in-m%25C3%25BCnster%2Fa-43297880&d=c0cgvjwHXMmVisdxPFAbKGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=2352e7d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.dw.com/en/germany-still-clueless-about-motive-for-fatal-van-attack-in-m%C3%BCnster/a-43297880</a><br />\n<br />\n唔係難民喎呢單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf90c4248acfd7cf80038d12a17567f88c78a622","tid":621388,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:43:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}